<p>Grapefruit oil is a light oil that is wonderful on the skin. It is pale yellow in colour and almost odourless making it ideal as a massage base for blending essential oils with or other carrier oils although it is a great oil to use on its own as a full massage oils or skin moisturising oil. Grapefruit is not a greasy oil and is popular as a base oil for creams and lotions, it is uplifting and almost gives energy and new life to the mind and body as well as the skin.</p>